description:
Blender 3.6 LTS offers two support options: the unofficial Cats add-on (recommended) and the official Cats add-on.

Known Incompatible Addons: Official Cats Blender Plugin and MMD Tools may cause conflicts as this version includes its own MMD Tools implementation.

The unofficial version includes several fixes not present in the official version.

Important: Do not ask for help with the unofficial version in the official Cats Discord server, and vice versa for the official version in the unofficial Discord.
